variant of 周遊|周游, to tour/to travel around

sentences.english: He spent his golden years traveling to many parts of the world.
sentences.chinese: 他通过周游世界度过了晚年的幸福时光。

sentences.english: Andersen also wrote travelogs4 while he traveled through different countries.
sentences.chinese: 安徒生在周游列国时也写了游记。

sentences.english: She toured the country, giving lecture after lecture.
sentences.chinese: 她周游全国，不断地举行讲座。

sentences.english: We'll travel round the world and we'll stay at the best hotels.
sentences.chinese: 就去周游世界，并且往最好的旅馆。

sentences.english: Thumbling, however, declined, and said he wanted to see the world first.
sentences.chinese: 大拇哥谢绝了，说自己想先周游世界。

sentences.english: A: To retire and travel around the world.
Andersen also wrote travelogs while he traveled through different countries.
sentences.chinese: 安徒生在周游列国时也写了游记。

sentences.english: I accompanied him on his European travel.
Thee Robinsons love seeing the world.
sentences.chinese: 罗宾逊一家喜欢周游世界。

sentences.english: Help Candice as she travels the world, learning and mastering divine new recipes.
sentences.chinese: 帮助王红，她周游世界，学习和掌握新的神圣的食谱。

sentences.english: Where is John? He's on a trip to Shanghai. He'll make a round-the-world trip.
sentences.chinese: 约翰在哪里？他去上海旅行楽他将周游世界。

sentences.english: Glen spent a small fortune on a tour round the world。
sentences.chinese: 格伦花了一笔小钱周游世界。

sentences.english: He was traveling around the world for months on end.
sentences.chinese: 几个月来他马不停蹄地周游世界。

sentences.english: Hannigan, free tour to all the ports in the world.
sentences.chinese: 汉尼根，免费周游世界上所有的港口。

sentences.english: All traversals of the editing model are recursive.
sentences.chinese: 编辑模式的所有周游都是递回性。

sentences.english: He vainly hope to travel round the world on foot.
